---
question: Can people buy abortion pills now to use later?
---
Yes, people buy abortion pills in advance, to have on hand in case of future need. This allows them to take the pills right away without waiting for shipping.&nbsp;

{% inlineLink action={discriminant: "internal", value: {page: "in-advance"}} %}Here is more information{% /inlineLink %} about services that offer pills in advance. For people who decide to use the pills later, these services will give instructions and provide support.
